            "text": "quod ex omni parte illis instaret interitus, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "“that destruction was threatening them on every side.” (Comp. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Isaiah 47:10",
            "children": []
          },
          {
