        "class": "",
        "text": "Through the advance of the ambush there came 10,000 picked men of all Israel \"from opposite to Gibeah\" (who now attacked in the rear the Benjaminites who were pursuing the flying army of Israel); \"and the contest became severe, since they (the Benjaminites) did not know that the calamity was coming upon them.\"",
        "children": []
